    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for daily commuting. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows noticeable signs of age, including some minor exterior scratches and wear on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, making it a solid choice for a buyer who prioritizes utility and value over a perfect aesthetic.",
